Alcohols
========

$$\begin{aligned}
\ce{ 2NaOH + I2  &-> NaOI + NaI + H2O } ) \times 4 \\
\ce{ \chemfig{  CH3-CH(-[2]OH)-R } + NaOI &->[oxidation] \chemfig{  CH3-C(=[2]O)-R } + NaI + H2O } \\
